    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-05-28T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-05-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="148"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d148">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">867.00/5–2847</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the <gloss type="from">Secretary of
                            State</gloss> to President <persName type="to">Truman</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-05-28">May 28,
                            1947</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I am attaching for your consideration a proposed basic agreement between the
                    United States and Turkey setting forth the general terms and conditions which
                    shall govern the furnishing of assistance to Turkey by the United States. To the
                    extent considered appropriate, the agreement follows the text of the proposed
                    agreement with Greece which Mr. Acheson sent to you on May 23, although a more
                    simple document is regarded as adequate to accomplish the more restricted nature
                    of the program of assistance to Turkey.</p>
                <p>If you approve the draft agreement,<note n="1" xml:id="d148fn1">The draft
                        agreement was dated May 28; see telegram 309, June 4, to Ankara, <ref
                            target="#pg_190">p. 190</ref>.</note> it will be sent to Ankara for
                    negotiation with the Turkish Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>G. C. <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
